reviews.text: Place to chill and be tipsy. I love this sportsbar. 😊
Great little bar in Wan Chai!
Great little Bar with lovely Staff. Shisha available for people who like it.

Horrible service!

I ordered a drink, paid for it and when I drank it, it didn't taste like what I had ordered.  So I asked for it to be replaced.  The bar told me that this is their version of the drink and told me that if I didn't like it, I could go somewhere else and drink. 

I would have expected that they would have made me something else. Or at least showed that they cared about their customers. 

I would NOT recommend going to this place!

------------------------
EDIT:  

Maybe you should post the whole video to show how you treat your potential customers when they don't order a drink.  (By slapping them.)   And this is not the first time I have been there... I have been there earlier and ordered plenty.  So I thought it would be a safe place to just sober up a bit. 

I thought I'd just write a review to recommend customers not to go there and not write about how your bartenders slap/manhandle people who are drunk... if you have the balls, I would like to see you post the whole video so that everyone can see that your bartender slapped me when I had not shown any sign of aggression. 

DEFINITELY WOULD NOT RECOMMEND THIS BAR.
Beer, shisha, screen to watch sports, what else ^^
